                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>We may collect various types of personal information from employees and job applicants, including but not not limited to:</p>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Personal Identifiers:</strong> Name, address, phone number, email address, date of birth, national identification numbers (e.g., SSS, PhilHealth, TIN), and other contact details.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Employment Information:</strong> Job title, department, employment history, qualifications, performance reviews, disciplinary records, and payroll information (bank details, salary, deductions).</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Educational Background:</strong> Degrees, certifications, and academic transcripts.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Health Information:</strong> Limited medical information relevant to workplace accommodations, sick leave, or occupational health and safety requirements, always in compliance with applicable laws.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Biometric Information:</strong> If collected for timekeeping or security purposes (e.g., fingerprint scans), this will be explicitly stated and justified.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Emergency Contact Information:</strong> Names and contact details of individuals to be contacted in case of an emergency.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Background Check Information:</strong> Information obtained during background checks, subject to your consent and legal requirements.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information related to your use of Company IT systems, networks, and communication tools (e.g., login times, websites visited on company devices, email communications).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">2. How We Collect Information</h2>
                <p>We collect information through various means, including:</p>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Directly from you during the application process, onboarding, and throughout your employment.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">From third parties, such as previous employers (with your consent), references, and background check providers.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Automatically through your use of Company systems and networks, in accordance with our IT Usage Policy.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">From publicly available sources where permissible by law.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
